
/*
 * This Hyperlambda code logs an error message when something goes wrong during an OpenAI invocation. It captures the error message, status, and the Hyperlambda representation of the error. 
 * 
 * 1. [log.error] - Logs an error message indicating something went wrong during the OpenAI invocation.
 * 2. [message] - Retrieves the error message from the HTTP POST response content.
 * 3. [status] - Retrieves the status code from the HTTP POST response.
 * 4. [error] - Converts the error details into a Hyperlambda string format for logging.
 */
log.error:Something went wrong while invoking OpenAI
   message:x:@http.post/*/content/*/error/*/message
   status:x:@http.post
   error:x:@lambda2hyper
